text: Ambatofinandrahana is a town in Ambatofinandrahana District in central Madagascar. It is a part of Amoron'i Mania Region. == Geography == This town lies at the Route nationale 35 from Morondava to Ivato at 67 km from Ivato. title: Ambatofinandrahana
